PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Gordon Lank, of North Wiltshire, Prince Edward Island, as a director of Marine Atlantic Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective June 15, 1990, in the place of John Arthur Hudson, whose term will expire.
